  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/1d28c745a1eba0a4655f57ea05af0734.webp?t=1729617160\" width=250 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mountain Hook is a simple, zen-like time-waster about scaling giant stone towers. It's best enjoyed with a podcast and your favorite snack as you ascend into the skies - flirt with gravity and let the real world pass by on the wind</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/633369e7e20ff304e710f49cd6e74f3e.poster.avif?t=1729617160\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/633369e7e20ff304e710f49cd6e74f3e.webm?t=1729617160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/633369e7e20ff304e710f49cd6e74f3e.mp4?t=1729617160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your route up each new mountain and take as many risks as you think necessary to reach the summit. Toss a few of your sticky explosives if you need to create some space and throw in the occasional back-flip simply because you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: </strong>Mountain Hook supports mouse and keyboard but was designed to be played with a pad for the most satisfying swing</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/fc3cc21acffa78de37c974d7c87ac6ae.webp?t=1729617160\" width=250 height=60 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A grappling hook with playfully satisfying swinging physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some explosives, in case you need to get creative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A genuinely pointless and risky back-flip ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Predefined challenge mountains to get you accustomed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock-able character customization options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support with configurable buttons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless, procedurally generated monoliths, begging to be tamed</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mountain Hook is the work of a solo developer. If you experience any issues, get in touch and I'll address them as soon as possible.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/1d28c745a1eba0a4655f57ea05af0734.webp?t=1729617160\" width=250 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mountain Hook is a simple, zen-like time-waster about scaling giant stone towers. It's best enjoyed with a podcast and your favorite snack as you ascend into the skies - flirt with gravity and let the real world pass by on the wind</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/633369e7e20ff304e710f49cd6e74f3e.poster.avif?t=1729617160\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/633369e7e20ff304e710f49cd6e74f3e.webm?t=1729617160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/633369e7e20ff304e710f49cd6e74f3e.mp4?t=1729617160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your route up each new mountain and take as many risks as you think necessary to reach the summit. Toss a few of your sticky explosives if you need to create some space and throw in the occasional back-flip simply because you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: </strong>Mountain Hook supports mouse and keyboard but was designed to be played with a pad for the most satisfying swing</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231030/extras/fc3cc21acffa78de37c974d7c87ac6ae.webp?t=1729617160\" width=250 height=60 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A grappling hook with playfully satisfying swinging physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some explosives, in case you need to get creative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A genuinely pointless and risky back-flip ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Predefined challenge mountains to get you accustomed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock-able character customization options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support with configurable buttons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless, procedurally generated monoliths, begging to be tamed</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mountain Hook is the work of a solo developer. If you experience any issues, get in touch and I'll address them as soon as possible.</i></p>",
